msgid "Set your time zone. This example uses Los Angeles."
msgstr ""

#: ../../guides/maintenance/time.rst:26
msgid ""
"To see a list of time zones, use the command: :command:`timedatectl list-"
"timezones | grep <locale>`"
msgstr ""

